{
  "stem": "1502.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And we were-- there were hundreds of thousands of people fleeing on the roads.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Besides all the Jews, many of the Belgians were fleeing towards France.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the Germans were the German Air Force-- was constantly attacking the roads.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were coming down with a dive-- dive bombers.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They would machine gun the roads.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Occasionally, they would machine gun the refugees.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And many people were lying dead in ditches along the-- along the road.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So it was-- it was very dangerous to walk on the roads at that time.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "The further we walked, the closer we-- we felt the front is getting to us, because the Germans were coming faster than we were walking.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "When we reached the French border, we heard the sound of heavy guns already in the back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We-- we stayed, I remember, we-- when we came to the French border, we didn't have where to sleep.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Each night, to sleep was a problem.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Somehow, we managed.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We found abandoned farms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We broke into the farms, and that's where we stayed overnight.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We came to the French border.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I always remember this very wonderful person, a very nice person-- Christian-- a Belgian-- who-- we were in a whole group.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Besides us, we were-- there were other people that we met on the road that we knew from before.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And he, without hesitations, he opened his house to us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And he-- he took us in-- all of us-- it was a group, maybe of more than 20 people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he was extremely nice.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he told us to feel at home.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "He fed us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "He gave us food-- as much as we wanted.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "He gave my parents his own bedroom.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "He was an extremely nice person.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
